    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>Hi Molly, the discussion about cookies has actually prompted (and inspired) me to bake. I never baked before, but I might as well start. A friend of mine once recommended on another way to relax by cooking for her and her husband, every night a fresh dish, which was never cooked by her before. I think its quite challenging to keep up and dig the recipes, but inspiring.</>Scouti</p>
