      <a href="https://orangette.net/2007/12/so-much-better/#comment-9589"><time class="comment-time" datetime="2007-12-26T20:03:00-05:00">Wednesday, December 26, 2007 at 8:03 pm</time></a>    </header>

    
    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I am glad you posted this- I have the exact same story, basically.  I saw this recipe two years ago, and would re-read the story from time to time, vowing one day to make them.  I did last week, and my husband and I tried one on the first day, another on the second day and then anxiously tried one the third day.  They really do evolve so nicely from a crisp cookie into something so rich and tender.  I could eat a box of those so I&#8217;m glad they are labor intensive!  </></>Happy Holidays:)</p>
    </div>

    <div class="reply">
