    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I LOVE the shape of these spoon cookies!</></>Congrats on finishing your book Molly.  My boyfriend is an author and I remember how crazy the house was during his last deadline&#8212;but then the weeks after that were filled with relaxation and deep breaths!  Congrats again and can&#8217;t wait to grab up a copy of your book next year! </></>Robin</p>
