    <div class="comment--content">
      <p>I made these for the first time the other day, using melted chocolate instead of jam and brought them to a committee meeting. They were devoured within minutes and I had two friends arguing over who could have the privalege of marrying me. Molly these are fantastic. Time consuming, but well worth it!</p>
